<div id='post-slider'><article class='full post' data-channel='tech' data-id='51845b78b589e4352a0d1222' data-subchannels='dev-design' data-topic='' data-velocity='954,1000,647,568,514' data-wp-id='1837975' id='story'>
<header class='article-header'>
<h1 class='title' href='http://mashable.com/2013/05/03/spark-core-add-wifi-to-anything/'>Add Wi-Fi to Practically Anything With This Arduino-Compatible Chip</h1>
<aside class='shares social'>
<div class='total-shares' data-index='0'>
<em>696</em>
<div class='caption'>Shares</div>
</div>
